T02TD2692E:257b-17: rim pa bzhin du lha'i rigs drug ni 'dod pa'i khams la de bzhin du stong stong brtsi bar bya'o //
T02TD2692E:257b-18: de bzhin du ri rab kyang yin te /
T02TD2692E:257b-24: nub kyi ba long spyod stong /
T02TD2692E:257b-25: byang gi sgra mi snyan stong /
T02TD2692E:257b-26: de bzhin tsha ba'i dmyal ba dang /
T02TD2692E:257b-30: de ni 'dod ba'i khams kyi stong rtsi lugs so //
T02TD2692E:257b-31: gzugs med kyi khams kyang de bzhin du yin no //
T02TD2692E:257b-32: dbang phyug chen po la dbang bgyid pa lags te zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:257b-33: stong spyi phud kyi khams la dbang mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2692E:257b-34: yang na de ni stong spyi phud kyi 'jig rten gyi khams yin te /
T02TD2692E:257b-35: mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pa chen po dbang sdud mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2692E:257b-36: btsun pa bcom ldan 'das bdag ni 'tshal na /
T02TD2692E:257b-37: stong gi 'jig rten gyi khams rnams su srung bar bgyid ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:257b-40: 'byung po rnams kyis kyang phan par byed pa dang /
T02TD2692E:257b-41: gnod par byed pa'i nges tshig bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar tshig zhus pa'o //
T02TD2692E:257b-42: srung bar bgyid ces pa ni /
T02TD2692E:257b-43: bcom ldan 'das kyi bka' las mi 'da' ba'o //
T02TD2692E:257b-44: yongs su skyob par bgyid cing /
T02TD2692E:257b-47: bde legs su 'gyur bar bgyid lags so zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:257b-48: bkra shis shing sems can thams cad la bde bar gnas par byas pa'o //
T02TD2692E:257b-49: btsun pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:257b-50: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga spangs shing /
T02TD2692E:258a-2: sems can thams cad kyi don la sprul pa'i skus khyab pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258a-3: bde bar gshegs pa chos kyi mnga' bdag ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:258a-4: bag chags kyi sgrib pa dang /
T02TD2692E:258a-5: shes bya'i sgrib pas ma gos te /
T02TD2692E:258a-6: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyis mi gos shing /
T02TD2692E:258a-9: de bzhin du gti mug dang /
T02TD2692E:258a-13: phrag dog rnams kyis mi tshugs shing bde bar gshegs te /
T02TD2692E:258a-14: lus pa med pas na bde bar gshegs pa ste /
T02TD2692E:258a-15: de bas na chos rang bzhin ni dngos po med cing rnyog pa med pa ste /
T02TD2692E:258a-17: rtag chad gnyis dang bral te /
T02TD2692E:258a-18: brjod pas kyang mi khyab pa ste /
T02TD2692E:258a-19: nam mkha' bzhin du sems can thams cad la khyab pas na /
T02TD2692E:258a-21: bcom ldan 'das ni stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams rnams su dbang phyug la mnga' mdzad pa lags te zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:258a-22: bzhi bcom skal ba dang ldan pa ste /
T02TD2692E:258a-23: ri rab la sogs pa 'jig rten gyi khams 'di stong stong brtsi ste /
T02TD2692E:258a-24: de ni stong spyi phud gyi 'jig rten gyi khams yin no //
T02TD2692E:258a-25: de bzhin du nyis 'gyur du brtsis pa ni stong bar ma'o //
T02TD2692E:258a-26: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams ni /
T02TD2692E:258a-27: de de'i sum 'gyur du brtsis pa ni stong gsum mo //
T02TD2692E:258a-28: chen po ni sems can thams cad bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258a-29: 'jig rten gyi khams ni mnyam por gzigs shing mnyam por bsten te /
T02TD2692E:258a-30: dge sdig la sogs pa gnas shing sems can gnas pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258a-31: de la sprul pa'i skus khyab ste /
T02TD2692E:258a-32: sems can rigs mi gcig pa'i phyir na rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs bstan pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258a-33: yang na sems can gyi don la der dbang mdzad de /
T02TD2692E:258a-34: theg pa sna tshogs bstan zhing yang dag pa'i byang chub kyi lam bstan pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258a-35: de ni tshangs pa'i tshig go //
T02TD2692E:258a-36: bcom ldan 'das kyang bzhed na zhes bya ba ni byams pa dang /
T02TD2692E:258a-39: btang snyoms bsgom zhing sems can rnams kyi don mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258a-40: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams rnams su zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:258b-0: sprul pa'i skus @258b kyang skad cig thang cig yud tsam gyis kyang /
T02TD2692E:258b-1: sems can gyi don mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258b-6: bde legs su 'gyur bar mdzad pa lags na zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:258b-7: mi dge ba bcu la 'gro bar yang srung ste mtho ris kyi lam bstan pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258b-9: 'jig rten dang da ltar byung ba rnams kyi 'tshe ba dang /
T02TD2692E:258b-10: ngan song gsum las 'thon par byed pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258b-11: mi dge ba bcu la 'gro ba yang bzung ste /
T02TD2692E:258b-12: de las ldog nas dge ba bcu la 'jug pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258b-13: dper na shing skam po 'gugs te ;
T02TD2692E:258b-14: khengs pa'i rang bzhin thabs kyis 'gugs pa bzhin du /
T02TD2692E:258b-15: khengs pa khro bo'i rigs kyang bcom ldan 'das kyi gzi brjid kyis kyang 'dul bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258b-16: yang na zhi ba ni bcom ldan 'das sangs rgyas dang chos dang dge 'dun gyi byin rlabs kyis zhi bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258b-19: yang dag pa'i ye shes thob par byed pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258b-20: yang na 'jig rten gyi khams 'di la /
T02TD2692E:258b-23: yid bde zhing phun sum tshogs pa yi dags rnams kyis kyang 'tshe bar mi byed pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258b-24: mdzad lags na zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:258b-25: bcom ldan 'das la tshangs pas yang nas yang du zhus pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258b-26: btsun pa bcom ldan 'das zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:258b-27: lan gcig mngon du zhugs te /
T02TD2692E:258b-28: lan gnyis ba ni da ltar zhu ste /
T02TD2692E:258b-30: lan gcig lan gnyis lan gsum du /
T02TD2692E:258b-31: tshangs pa rnams kyis yang dang yang du zhus pa'o //
T02TD2692E:258b-32: de nas bcom ldan 'das mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pa la cang mi gsung bas gnang ngo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:258b-33: de nas ni tshangs pas smras pa'i de nas so //
T02TD2692E:258b-34: sems can rnams la dmigs nas rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin ma zhal nas byung ste /
T02TD2692E:258b-35: mam gyi yi ge'i rang bzhin las nam mkha' bzhin du khyab pa /
T02TD2692E:258b-37: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems can thams cad kyi sdug bsngal dang bral ba dang /
T02TD2692E:258b-38: stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa /
T02TD2692E:259a-0: ngo bo dang bral zhing gang gis brjod du med pa de ni bcom ldan 'das sh'akya thub pa'i zhal nas @259a * //
T02TD2692E:259a-6: sangs rgyas lnga'i dbu rgyan dang bcas pa /
T02TD2692E:259a-8: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD2692E:259a-12: / phyag dang po'i g-yas g-yon gnyis na chos kyi rgyal po'i phyag rgya mdzad pa /
T02TD2692E:259a-13: de'i 'og ma gnyis kyis byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
T02TD2692E:259a-14: de'i 'og ma gnyis kyis mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
T02TD2692E:259a-15: g-yas pa'i tha mas mchod sbyin gyi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
T02TD2692E:259a-16: g-yon pas skyabs sbyin phyag rgya'o //
T02TD2692E:259a-17: zhabs padma skyil krung du bzhugs pa /
T02TD2692E:259a-19: shes rab kyi ngo bo na so sor rtog pa'i ye shes thabs kyi ngo bo yang rig sngags kyi rgyal mo'o //
T02TD2692E:259a-20: 'du shes kyi phung po padma gsung gi rigs me'i khams ro'i skye mched do //
T02TD2692E:259a-22: zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs shing nyi ma'i 'od zer dang ldan pa /
T02TD2692E:259a-23: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i 'khor dang bcas shing /
T02TD2692E:259a-24: rin po che sna bdun gyi gzhal med khang dang bcas nas byung ba'o //
T02TD2692E:259a-25: bcom ldan 'das kyis cang mi gsung zhing sems can gyi don la tshangs pa la sogs pas zhus pa la ting nge 'dzin gnang ba'o //
T02TD2692E:259a-26: de nas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:259a-27: bcom ldan 'das kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis gnang ba de nas so //
T02TD2692E:259a-28: mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pas bcom ldan 'das kyis cang mi gsung bas gnang bar rig nas /
T02TD2692E:259a-29: de nyid du mi snang bar gyur to zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:259a-30: stong spyi phud kyi rgyal po tshangs pas mngon par shes pas ting nge 'dzin gyis gnang bar shes so //
T02TD2692E:259a-31: de nas zhes bya ba ni tshangs pas mngon par shes pa'i de nas so //
T02TD2692E:259a-32: bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong rnams la bka' stsal pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:259a-35: nyan thos dgra bcom pa dang /
T02TD2692E:259a-40: de la sogs pa mi dang /
T02TD2692E:259a-41: lha dang lha ma yin dang /
T02TD2692E:259b-0: 'byung po mang po 'dul ba'i 'khor gyi nang du bcom ldan @259b 'das sh'akya seng ges bka' stsal to /
T02TD2692E:259b-1: dge slong dag stong spyi phud kyi rgyal po tshangs ris kyi lha rnams dang bcas pa dang zhes bya ba ni gzugs kyi khams kyi lha gnas ris bcu bdun dang ngo //
T02TD2692E:259b-2: lha'i dbang po brgya byin sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha rnams dang bcas pa dang zhes bya ba ni 'dod pa'i khams sum cu rtsa gsum nas yar la bgrangs pa lnga dang bcas pa'o //
T02TD2692E:259b-3: rgyal po chen po bzhi'i ris kyi lha rnams dang bcas pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:259b-4: rgyal chen bzhi'i ris nas mar la bgrangs pa /
T02TD2692E:259b-6: gser gyi ri bdun phreng thogs kyi lha rnams la sogs pa'i 'dod pa'i khams kyi lha'i bu rnams dang thabs cig go //
T02TD2692E:259b-7: rgyal po bzhi ni ri rab kyi lcog la gnas pa'o //
T02TD2692E:259b-8: gnod sbyin gyi ded dpon chen po nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang /
T02TD2692E:259b-10: g-yog 'khor dang bcas pa rnams zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:259b-11: gdon gyi rigs nyi shu rtsa drug dpon re re dang bcas pa stong phrag brgyad cu lha'i gdon la sogs pa re re yang stong phrag brgyad cu brgyad cu'o //
T02TD2692E:259b-12: de rnams dang thabs cig tu'o //
T02TD2692E:259b-14: mi mjed kyi bdag pos nga la 'di skad ces smras so zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:259b-15: sems can gyi don la rig sngags kyi tshig smras so zhes pa'o //
T02TD2692E:259b-16: btsun pa bcom ldan 'das zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:259b-17: mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pas bcom ldan 'das la lan gcig lan gnyis /
T02TD2692E:259b-18: lan gsum zhus pa'i lan bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong rnams la bshad pa'o //
T02TD2692E:259b-19: mnga' mdzad pa lags te zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:259b-20: chos kyi rang bzhin gyis stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams sprul pa'i skus khyab pa'o //
T02TD2692E:259b-21: bcom ldan 'das kyang bzhed na zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:259b-22: tshangs pas yang nas yang du zhus pa'i tshig dge slong rnams la smras pa /
T02TD2692E:259b-23: lan gsum zhus pa'o zhes smras pa'o //
T02TD2692E:259b-24: bde legs su gyur par mdzad du gsol zhes gsol to zhes bya ba ni sems can gyi don la sprul pa dang /
T02TD2692E:259b-25: bde legs su gyur cig ces pa'o //
T02TD2692E:259b-26: dge slong dag ngas kyang mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pa la cang mi gsung bas gnang ngo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:259b-27: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi sems can don la /
T02TD2692E:260a-1: cig ma'i ting nge 'dzin gyis rig sngags 'phros pas 'gro ba ris drug gi don mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2692E:260a-2: de nas mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pas cang mi gsung bas gnang bar rig / nas de nyid du mi snang bar gyur to zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:260a-3: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa'i de nas te /
T02TD2692E:260a-4: de mngon par shes nas tshangs pa la sogs pas kyang /
T02TD2692E:260a-6: dge slong dag rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags chen mo rjes su 'dzin pa 'di zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:260a-7: bcom ldan 'das gyi rig sngags kyi nges tshig smras te /
T02TD2692E:260a-10: rgyal mo ni bdud rnams kyis mi tshugs te /
T02TD2692E:260a-12: gsang ba ni stong pa nyid yin te /
T02TD2692E:260a-13: khyab che ba mi dmigs pa rdo rje'i rang bzhin yin te /
T02TD2692E:260a-14: ngag gis kyang smra bar mi nus te /
T02TD2692E:260a-15: ngo bo rnam par dag pa chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes mi dmigs pa ste gsang ba'o ;
T02TD2692E:260a-20: chos thams cad kyang sgyu ma lta bu'o //
T02TD2692E:260a-21: sangs rgyas rnams kyang sgyu ma lta bu'o //
T02TD2692E:260a-22: bcom ldan 'das kyis kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa brgyad stong pa las /
T02TD2692E:260a-23: stong gsum gyi stong chen po 'jig rten gyi khams kyang sgyu ma lta bu ste /
T02TD2692E:260a-28: rnam par shes pa rnams kyang rmi lam lta bu /
T02TD2692E:260a-33: rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu'o zhes gsungs so //
T02TD2692E:260a-34: yang na sngags ni thams cad la khyab ste sprul pa'i sku'i rang bzhin gyis sems can rnams kyi don mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2692E:260a-35: rjes su 'dzin pa ni rig sngags kyi rgyas btab ste /
T02TD2692E:260a-40: mi la sogs pa rjes su 'dzin te /
T02TD2692E:260a-41: de'i ye shes kyi lam gyis /
T02TD2692E:260a-43: thun mong ma yin pa'i 'bras bu thob ba'o //
T02TD2692E:260a-44: rig sngags 'di ni yang dag pa'i ye shes yin no //
T02TD2692E:260a-45: 'das pa'i de bzhin gshegs ba dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang gsungs so zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:260b-1: gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed kyi bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong mar me mdzad la sogs pa sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2692E:260b-2: rjes su yi rang ste 'di'i lam nas sangs rgyas pa'o //
T02TD2692E:260b-3: ma 'ongs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyang gsung bar 'gyur ro zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:260b-4: ma 'ongs pa rnams ni bcom ldan 'das byams ba la sogs pa yin te /
T02TD2692E:260b-5: de bzhin du de'i lam nas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob pa'o //
T02TD2692E:260b-6: da ltar byung ba na yang 'di lta ste /
T02TD2692E:260b-7: sangs rgyas kyi byang chub nyid la phan par bya ba'i phyir da ltar nga nyid kyis bshad do zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:260b-8: smon lam gyi stobs kyis 'di'i tshe 'di la sems can gyi don la /
T02TD2692E:260b-9: sh'akya seng ges kyang gsungs shing rjes su yi rang ste /
T02TD2692E:260b-10: 'di'i lam yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob pa'o //
T02TD2692E:260b-11: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin pa'i tshangs pa la sogs pas rig sngags zhu ba'i gnas skabs te gsum pa'o //
T02TD2692E:260b-12: rig sngags kyi nges tshig gi rtags dang po rdzogs so /
T02TD2692E:260b-14: // / de nas zhes bya ba ni 'das pa dang /
T02TD2692E:260b-16: da ltar bzhugs pas gsungs pa'i de nas so //
T02TD2692E:260b-17: bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:260b-18: gsang sngags kyi tshig 'di zung shig ces gsungs nas /
T02TD2692E:260b-19: kun dga' bo la bcom ldan 'das kyis gtad pa'o //
T02TD2692E:260b-20: kun dga' bo khyod kyis rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin ma 'di zung shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:260b-21: sku gsum gyi rang bzhin la sems can rnams kyi don mdzad pa gsang sngags kyi tshig gis /
T02TD2692E:260b-22: ma rig pa'i mun pa bsal te /
T02TD2692E:260b-24: sku gsung thugs kyis bzung nas sems can rnams kyi don mdzad do zhes pa'o //
T02TD2692E:260b-25: tshongs shig / lhogs shig / shod cig / kun chub par gyis shig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:260b-26: nga'i bka' las ma 'das par byas shing /
T02TD2692E:260b-27: sems can gyi don la nga mya ngan las 'das nas kyang /
T02TD2692E:260b-28: gsungs shig rjes su yi rang zhing sems can thams cad la ston cig ces bya ba'o //
T02TD2692E:261a-1: ltar khyod kyis de ltar bzung nas sems can gyi don la tshig gzung bar gyis shig ces pa'o //
T02TD2692E:261a-2: kun dga' bo zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:261a-3: bcom ldan 'das kyis yang dang yang du gsungs pa'o //
T02TD2692E:261a-4: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin ma 'di ni zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:261a-8: ye shes kyi tshogs rnam par dag pa /
T02TD2692E:261a-10: sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral ba'o //
T02TD2692E:261a-11: 'khor bzhi po rnams kyi don dang /
T02TD2692E:261a-14: bde bar reg par gnas par 'gyur ro zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:261a-15: med pa yod par byed de /
T02TD2692E:261a-16: yod pa rnams kyang med par byed pa'o //
T02TD2692E:261a-17: bkra mi shis pa bkra shis pa ste /
T02TD2692E:261a-18: brjed pa rnams kyang dran pa rnyed de /
T02TD2692E:261a-19: shes rab chud ba rnams kyang shes rab dang ldan pa /
T02TD2692E:261a-21: tshe thung ba rnams kyang tshe ring bar byed de /
T02TD2692E:261a-23: mi bde ba yang bde bar byed de /
T02TD2692E:261a-24: ma rungs pa'i gdon rnams kyis /
T02TD2692E:261a-26: chos byed du mi ster ba'i gdon rnams 'joms shing /
T02TD2692E:261a-27: tshig tu brjod pa tsam gyis kyang /
T02TD2692E:261a-33: lugs sku la sogs pa rab tu gnas par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2692E:261a-34: yang na 'khor bzhi la sogs pa la bar chod med cing bde bar bgyid do //
T02TD2692E:261a-36: padma'i rigs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs te /
T02TD2692E:261a-37: mtshon pa ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes so //
T02TD2692E:261a-38: mtshon byed ni rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin pa'o //
T02TD2692E:261a-39: phung po ni gzugs kyi phung po'o //
T02TD2692E:261a-40: sa'i khams ni mig gi skye mched /
T02TD2692E:261a-41: ye shes lnga'i ngo bo nyid /
T02TD2692E:261a-42: sangs rgyas lnga'i dbu rgyan can /
T02TD2692E:261a-47: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa ;
T02TD2692E:261a-48: zhal g-yas mthing ga / g-yon dmar ba /
T02TD2692E:261a-53: g-yon pa gsum na rin po che dang /
T02TD2692E:261a-57: g-yon bskum pas padma'i steng na /
T02TD2692E:261b-1: nyi ma'i 'od dang ldan pa ste /

T02TD2692E:279b-33: de 'og rdo rje sa gzhi la //
T02TD2692E:279b-34: gzhal yas khang gi dbus su shes //
T02TD2692E:279b-35: dbus su sna tshogs padma ste //
T02TD2692E:279b-36: phyir ni 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad do //
T02TD2692E:279b-37: de phyir lha snam zlum po ste //
T02TD2692E:279b-38: gza' dang rgyu skar gnas pa'o //
T02TD2692E:279b-39: phyi rol lha snam gru bzhi la //
T02TD2692E:279b-40: phyogs skyong yang ni der gnas so //
T02TD2692E:279b-41: shar dang lho dang nub dang ni //
T02TD2692E:279b-42: byang gi sgo bzhi dang po la //
T02TD2692E:279b-43: rgyal po bzhi yang der bzhugs so //
T02TD2692E:279b-44: dbus su sna tshogs padma la //
T02TD2692E:279b-45: ye shes lha mo lnga yang bzhugs //
T02TD2692E:279b-46: mtshams bzhi padma stong pa la //
T02TD2692E:279b-47: mchod pa'i lha mo bzhi gnas so //
T02TD2692E:279b-48: dbus su lte ba zla ba'i gdan //
T02TD2692E:279b-49: gsang sngags 'dzin ma der bzhugs so //
T02TD2692E:279b-51: rig sngags bum pa lnga po ste //
T02TD2692E:279b-52: mtshan ma ldan zhing nag po med //
T02TD2692E:280a-2: dbyibs ni legs shing lto ba che //
T02TD2692E:280a-3: de lta bu yi mtshan ldan la //
T02TD2692E:280a-4: aa ka ru 'am gu gu la bdug par bya //
T02TD2692E:280a-5: rin chen lnga dang 'bru lnga dang //
T02TD2692E:280a-6: dri lnga sman lnga de bzhin te //
T02TD2692E:280a-7: 'bras bu can gyi shing lnga yi //
T02TD2692E:280a-8: lo mas kha la rnam bar brgyan //
T02TD2692E:280a-9: bdud rtsi lnga dang snying po lnga //
T02TD2692E:280a-10: de bzhin mgul chings gdugs kyis brgyan //
T02TD2692E:280a-11: rim bzhin dkyil 'khor dgod par bya //
T02TD2692E:280a-12: yan lag dang ni gtor ma dang //
T02TD2692E:280a-13: bdag gis 'dir ni ma bshad de //
T02TD2692E:280a-14: gzhan la ltos la shes par gyis //
T02TD2692E:280a-15: rdo rje slob dpon dge slong gis ;
T02TD2692E:280a-16: / kha zas dkar po bsten nas su //
T02TD2692E:280a-17: cho ga yang dag bsam par gyis //
T02TD2692E:280a-18: khengs pa med cing nga rgyal spang //
T02TD2692E:280a-19: nyon mongs shas ni mi che zhing //
T02TD2692E:280a-20: byams dang snying rje dga' ba dang //
T02TD2692E:280a-21: btang snyoms la ni yang dag 'jug / yi ge bzhi ba'i sngags kyis ni //
T02TD2692E:280a-22: dgug pa gzhug pa bcing ba dang //
T02TD2692E:280a-23: ye shes lha ni dgyes par 'gyur /
T02TD2692E:280a-24: srom [?] mkhan la sogs bsang gtor bya //
T02TD2692E:280a-25: bsnyen pa cho ga yang dag bzung //
T02TD2692E:280a-26: mchod bstod la sogs byas nas su //
T02TD2692E:280a-27: thun gtor la sogs gtang bar bya //
T02TD2692E:280a-28: phyogs skyong bcu dang rgyal po dang //
T02TD2692E:280a-29: gza' dang skar ma 'byung po rnams //
T02TD2692E:280a-30: rjes mthun gtor ma byin nas su //
T02TD2692E:280a-31: de la mchod pa bstod pa bya //
T02TD2692E:280a-32: rdo rje slob dpon bka' drin gyis //
T02TD2692E:280a-33: nad pa yul 'khor yang dag bsrung //
T02TD2692E:280a-34: sems can la ni snying rje'i phyir //
T02TD2692E:280a-35: rim gro'i cho ga yang dag bshad //
T02TD2692E:280a-36: de ni dkyil 'khor byed pa'i thabs so //
T02TD2692E:280a-37: 'khor lo rim pa bcu bris la //
T02TD2692E:280a-38: sngar bshad las kyi snying po dgod //
T02TD2692E:280a-39: phyi rol 'khor lo'i ra ba la //
T02TD2692E:280a-40: phyag mtshan phyag rgya dgod pa ste //
T02TD2692E:280a-41: mnyam gzhag byang chub mchog dang ni //
T02TD2692E:280a-42: chos 'chad skyab sbyin mchog sbyin dang //
T02TD2692E:280a-43: sa gnon chos sbyin phyag skor ba //
T02TD2692E:280a-44: bum rten rdo rje rin chen dang //
T02TD2692E:280a-45: ral gri'i steng na rdo rje dang //
T02TD2692E:280a-46: de bzhin padma de bzhin no //
T02TD2692E:280a-47: 'khor lo lcags kyu rdo rje dang //
T02TD2692E:280a-48: de bzhin 'khor lo'i phyag rgyas bskor //
T02TD2692E:280a-49: padma'i steng na phyag mtshan gnas //
T02TD2692E:280a-50: sdong bu dar gyis bcings pa la //
T02TD2692E:280b-0: rgyas par yang ni bri @280b bar bya //
T02TD2692E:280b-1: 'khor lo nyi po zlum po la //
T02TD2692E:280b-2: padma rdo rje yang dag bri //
T02TD2692E:280b-3: bde bar gsang sngags yi ge dgod par bya //
T02TD2692E:280b-4: de nang gsum po mu khyud la //
T02TD2692E:280b-5: sngar bshad sngags kyis bskor bar bya //
T02TD2692E:280b-6: de nang mu khyud gcig pu la //
T02TD2692E:280b-7: 'khor lo'i rim pa de bzhin shes //
T02TD2692E:280b-8: 'khor lo'i nang du ma khyud de /
T02TD2692E:280b-9: sngar bshad sngags ni bri ba'o //
T02TD2692E:280b-10: de yi nang na 'khor lo la /
T02TD2692E:280b-12: 'khor lo'i lte bar mu khyud dang //
T02TD2692E:280b-13: snying po yi ni sngags bzhin no //
T02TD2692E:280b-14: lte sngags yi ge bri ba ste /
T02TD2692E:280b-15: blo dang ldan pas bri bar bya //
T02TD2692E:280b-16: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags kyi rjes su 'dzin pa'i dkyil 'khor dang ;
T02TD2692E:280b-17: srung ba'i 'khor lo bshad pa'i gnas skabs te bdun pa'o /
T02TD2692E:280b-19: // / yongs su bskyab pa dang zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni /
T02TD2692E:280b-20: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi bka' dang /
T02TD2692E:280b-21: rig sngags kyi bden pa dang /
T02TD2692E:280b-22: srung ba de rnams kyis kyang /
T02TD2692E:280b-23: sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral zhing bde bar gnas te /
T02TD2692E:280b-24: srung ba des yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob pa'o //
T02TD2692E:280b-25: 'byung po thams cad bzlog par bya'o zhes bya ba ni bden pa 'dis lha'i gdon la sogs pa thams cad kyis mi tshugs shing /
T02TD2692E:280b-26: bde bar gnas shing 'jigs pa med par gnas pa'o //
T02TD2692E:280b-27: gzi brjid 'phrog pa rnams bzlog par bya'o zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:280b-28: ma rungs pa'i byis pa'i gdon rnams yin te /
T02TD2692E:280b-30: skyes nas lo bcu gnyis bar du 'dzin pa'o //
T02TD2692E:280b-31: de'i phyir nas sems can la gzi byin 'phrog pa yin te /
T02TD2692E:280b-32: bden pa de yis bde bar gnas shing ;
T02TD2692E:280b-35: lo bcu gnyis nas kyang bde bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2692E:280b-36: bden pa dang bden pa'i tshig ces ba bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:280b-37: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi bka' dang /
T02TD2692E:280b-38: rig sngags kyi bden pas bde bar gnas te the tshom med de //
T02TD2692E:280b-39: gang gis bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:280b-42: da ltar byung ba'i sangs rgyas rnams yin te /
T02TD2692E:280b-43: 'das pa rnams ni mar me mdzad la sogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
T02TD2692E:281a-1: 'ongs pa rnams kyang de bzhin du byams pa la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2692E:281a-2: da ltar yod pa'i sh'akya thub pas kyang bdud bzhi bcom nas ston par byas pa'o //
T02TD2692E:281a-5: gti mug zad par bya ba'i phyir ni zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:281a-6: 'dod chags ni phung po'i bdud de /
T02TD2692E:281a-7: zhe sdang ni nyon mongs pa'i bdud do //
T02TD2692E:281a-8: gti mug ni 'chi bdag gi bdud yin te /
T02TD2692E:281a-9: de 'joms pa ni lha'i bu'i bdud do //
T02TD2692E:281a-10: sangs rgyas rnams kyis bdud bzhi bcom zhing /
T02TD2692E:281a-11: 'khor ba ma lus par bcom zhing chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'o //
T02TD2692E:281a-12: chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong bstan pa dang zhes bya ba'i bdud bzhi bcom nas /
T02TD2692E:281a-14: sprul pa'i skus khyab nas chos ston pa'o //
T02TD2692E:281a-15: bshad pa dang brjod pa'i zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:281a-16: chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong bstan nas /
T02TD2692E:281a-18: de yang sems can gyi don la yin no //
T02TD2692E:281a-19: bden pa dang bden pa'i tshig des ming 'di zhes bya ba'i nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi zad par gyur cig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:281a-20: de bzhin du de'i bden pas /
T02TD2692E:281a-21: bdag dang sems can thams cad bde bar 'gyur zhing /
T02TD2692E:281a-22: nad thams cad zhi bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2692E:281a-23: nad med par gyur cig ; zhi bar gyur cig / rab tu zhi bar gyur cig ces bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:281a-24: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin pa 'dis /
T02TD2692E:281a-25: nad thams cad 'joms par byas te /
T02TD2692E:281a-26: gdon thams cad brlag par byas nas /
T02TD2692E:281a-30: 'dus pa dang ldan pa la sogs pa'i nad rigs mi gcig pa bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi bcom nas /
T02TD2692E:281a-31: nad pa rnams la bde bar gnas par byed pa'o //
T02TD2692E:281a-32: bden pa 'di yis kyang yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu thob pa'o //
T02TD2692E:281a-33: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin ma'i bden pa'i tshig gis nad pa gso ba'i gnas skabs te brgyad pa'o /
T02TD2692E:281a-35: // / de skad ces bka' stsal nas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:281a-36: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin ma'i tshig 'di bka' stsal pa'o //
T02TD2692E:281a-37: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos /
T02TD2692E:281b-0: btsun pa de bzhin @281b bgyi'o zhes bya ba gsol to zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:281b-1: kun dga' bos thugs su chud nas /
T02TD2692E:281b-4: ras la bris nas rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags te zhes bya ba'o //
T02TD2692E:281b-5: bcom ldan 'das kyi ltar mnyan nas /
T02TD2692E:281b-6: yangs pa'i grong khyer du song ste zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:281b-7: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos sems can thams cad dang /
T02TD2692E:281b-8: yangs pa can gyi sems can rnams kyi /
T02TD2692E:281b-12: chos rnams kyang bshad du mi btub cing /
T02TD2692E:281b-13: ma rungs pa 'byung po rnams kyis khyer ba'i phyir ro //
T02TD2692E:281b-14: sgo yi them pa la rkang pa bzhag nas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:281b-15: grong khyer yangs pa can gyi dbus su yul lha'i them pa la gnas nas /
T02TD2692E:281b-16: rig sngags kyi nga rgyal byas nas /
T02TD2692E:281b-17: rgyal mtshan lag na thogs nas /
T02TD2692E:281b-19: gsang sngags kyi gzhi 'di dag dang /
T02TD2692E:281b-20: tshigs su bcad pa 'di dag kyang smras so zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:281b-21: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo'i zhal nas /
T02TD2692E:281b-22: nyi ma stong phrag brgya shar ba bzhin du /
T02TD2692E:281b-23: 'od zer re res rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin ma khro bo'i tshul gyis bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros te /
T02TD2692E:281b-24: grong khyer yangs pa can du zhugs pa'i lha 'dre rnams de'i 'od zer gyi khro bos lha 'dre rnams phyir phyung ste /
T02TD2692E:281b-25: rig sngags kyi dmod mos mi theg pas gzugs sna tshogs ston cing bros so //
T02TD2692E:281b-29: zhes pa la sogs pa las so //
T02TD2692E:281b-30: de'i sngags yungs kar bsres la phyogs bzhir gtor bas lha 'dre thams cad kyis mi tshugs so //
T02TD2692E:281b-31: nir gatstsha ta nir gatstsha ta la sogs pa'i sngags kyis /
T02TD2692E:281b-32: seng ldeng gi me phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhir spar la mtshams bzhi nas blangs la /
T02TD2692E:281b-35: shing tsher ma can bsres la me'i nang du gtor ro //
T02TD2692E:281b-36: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi nas chu gtor ro //
T02TD2692E:281b-37: de na zhugs pa'i 'byung po rnams kyis mi tshugs shing 'byung ngo //
T02TD2692E:281b-38: sum su la sogs pa'i sngags kyis srung skud sna lnga bsngags shing mdud pa bor te /
T02TD2692E:281b-39: de bsrung bar byas na nad thams cad kyis mi tshugs shing /
T02TD2692E:282a-2: su mu ru su mu ru zhes bya ba'i sngags ni rig sngags kyi snying po bstan to //
T02TD2692E:282a-3: de yang padma'i rigs kyi lam rigs so //
T02TD2692E:282a-4: mtshon pa ni bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes so //
T02TD2692E:282a-5: mtshon byed ni rig sngags kyi bdag nyid do //
T02TD2692E:282a-6: phung po ni 'du byed kyi phung po ste /
T02TD2692E:282a-7: khams ni rlung gi khams so //
T02TD2692E:282a-8: skye mched ni lus kyi skye mched do //
T02TD2692E:282a-10: sangs rgyas lnga'i dbu rgyan can /
T02TD2692E:282a-11: spyan gsum pa sku mdog ljang gu / zhal gsum pa /
T02TD2692E:282a-19: g-yon gsum na bsnams pa ni /
T02TD2692E:282a-25: padma'i steng na zla ba'i gdan la nyi ma'i 'od dang ldan pa ;
T02TD2692E:282a-26: 'dzum pa'i zhal dang ldan par bzhugs so //
T02TD2692E:282a-27: rig sngags kyi rigs ni gang zhe na /
T02TD2692E:282a-29: su mu ru su mu ru la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2692E:282a-30: de dag sngags rnams grub par 'gyur //
T02TD2692E:282a-32: gsang sngags kyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa la sogs pa'o//
T02TD2692E:282a-33: sangs rgyas rnams kyis byin rlabs dang /
T02TD2692E:282a-34: rig sngags gsang sngags rnams kyis byin brlabs pa /
T02TD2692E:282a-35: rnam par dag pa 'di 'das pa dang /
T02TD2692E:282a-37: da ltar yod pa rnams kyi bka' dang /
T02TD2692E:282a-38: rig sngags kyi chos bden pas /
T02TD2692E:282a-39: grong khyer yangs pa can srung zhing skyob pa dang /
T02TD2692E:282a-43: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:282a-44: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin ma bka' stsal to zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:282a-45: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:282a-46: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po lag na rdo rje la sogs pa /
T02TD2692E:282a-47: bye ba khrag khrig stong phrag brgyad do //
T02TD2692E:282a-48: nyan thos kyang de bzhin du sh'a ri'i bu la sogs pa nyis brgya lnga bcu dang ngo //
T02TD2692E:282b-0: dge @282b bsnyen ma la sogs pa mang po dang thabs cig tu'o //
T02TD2692E:282b-1: mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pa dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:282b-2: tshangs ris kyi lha rnams dang /
T02TD2692E:282b-3: gzugs kyi khams kyi lha rnams dang thabs cig go //
T02TD2692E:282b-4: lha dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:282b-5: lha'i dbang po brgya byin sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha rnams dang /
T02TD2692E:282b-6: rgyal po chen po bzhi dang /
T02TD2692E:282b-7: rgyal chen bzhi'i lha rnams dang zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:282b-8: lha ma yin gyi rgyal po thags zangs ris la sogs pa lha ma yin mang po dang /
T02TD2692E:282b-9: gnod sbyin gyi ded dpon nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang /
T02TD2692E:282b-10: dri zar bcas pa'i zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:282b-11: dri za'i rgyal po zur phud lnga pa g-yog du ma dang bcas pa dang 'phrog ma bu dang bcas pa /
T02TD2692E:282b-12: g-yog 'khor dang bcas pa rnams dang /
T02TD2692E:282b-13: 'jig rten yi rangs te zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:282b-14: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi'o //
T02TD2692E:282b-15: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD2692E:282b-24: lha ma yin la sogs pa'o //
T02TD2692E:282b-25: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin ma'o //
T02TD2692E:282b-26: grong khyer yangs pa can na zhugs pa'i 'byung po rnams phyir btang ba'i phyir gnas skabs te dgu pa'o /
T02TD2692E:282b-28: // / padma'i rigs lnga bstan pa'i brtags pa ste gnyis pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2692E:282b-30: // / rig sngags kyi rgyal mo chen mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin ma'i mdo'i 'bum 'grel slob dpon chen po las kyi rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2692E:282b-32: // / rig sngags kyi rgyal mo gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin ma'i mdo'i 'bum 'grel pandi ta mkhas pa chen po mi mnyam rdo rje'i sras /
T02TD2692E:282b-33: pandi ta don yod rdo rjes /
T02TD2692E:282b-34: jo mo sgrol mas zhabs kyis bcags pa /
T02TD2692E:282b-35: tshangs pa'i 'byung gnas rdo lung dgon par rang 'gyur mdzad pa'o /
T02TD2692E:282b-37: // /'di bsgyur bsod nams gang thob pa //
T02TD2692E:282b-38: de yis khams srid gsum du ni //
T02TD2692E:282b-39: gsang sngags rjes su 'dzin ma yi //
T02TD2692E:282b-40: dngos grub go 'phang myur thob shog //
